{"tid":808783,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪/北海道災後交通集中討論區5","createTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T13:42:33.000Z","uid":60924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"02b47dba98d0930d220d6c34c569eca6ddb70e5f","tid":808783,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"5應該完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be71b69edc2773c287d4675ea9e28133a62c9b24","tid":808783,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飛開大阪都知道T2 係樂桃同春秋航空天下<br />\n講真係PEACH 今次今快復飛國內線係有問題<br />\n其實係將人流分流去神户 <br />\n國際線復飛係重要(好多出口貨係KIA出貨)<br />\n另外佢條橋係另一半行到車係無問題<br />\n南海電鐵就死哂啦<br />\n但係JR 應該行到 單線<br />\n照睇日本拍出來片<br />\n但日本性格好怕狽飛<br />\n唔搞到100%佢都唔出手</blockquote>你究竟有冇親身搭過條鐵㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>JR同南海share 路軌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>其實而家係兩條路軌死曬定死一邊？</blockquote><br />\n死曬<br />\n<br />\n同社などによると、連絡橋の道路（下り線）の橋桁が、タンカー衝突で数メートル押し込まれた。この部分の道路から約２．５メートル下にある線路は、鉄板で囲まれた鉄道桁に敷設されている。上部の道路桁とともに鉄道桁も押し込まれ、約５０センチ横ずれしたとみられる。この影響で<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上下線２本のレールもゆがみ、架線も損傷したという</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"01a7498ba17f995bf425471c7d05d90992782d0c","tid":808783,"uid":42881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"架線有損壞，要整的話首要被撞行車橋移正位，先再整鐵路送電線<br />\n<br />\n但更重要係，成個地底站應該俾海水浸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/230651_8079c32254abfa5d7ca6981f22087bad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F230651_8079c32254abfa5d7ca6981f22087bad.jpg&h=71672f69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68a43ad5f8bf7077e6e53b80f633fd3203b6ccc5","tid":808783,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4839b1b15d33681ee184aa170d6cb4344d1cd9b","tid":808783,"uid":88081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"條鐵路係用龍門架式電線桿，橫跨哂出入兩條線，條斷橋撞冧左電線桿，出入兩線都會冇電。同埋路軌撞歪左要重舖架，都要移走斷橋先<br />\n仲有關空車站入邊停電+水浸"},{"pid":"0e2a1ea02634c05a72a7cccbce99488da77ad82e","tid":808783,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"Peach或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"28697e9305a0e08ab96de25aab3555746e6fa4b5","tid":808783,"uid":53643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b47dba98d0930d220d6c34c569eca6ddb70e5f","tid":808783,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"5應該完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5e23d1cf7fb81916d6c45701a313512c9622bc","tid":808783,"uid":60924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5應該完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔想有6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl